# statistic cmd
```
# mint num
cat wallet.txt| wc -l
# address num
sort wallet.txt | uniq | wc -l
# rank
# mint num
cat wallet.txt| wc -l
# address num
sort wallet.txt | uniq | wc -l
# rank
sort wallet.txt | uniq -c | sort -k1,1n
```
